  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      MORPHEOS is a multicenter, randomized, unblinded study, for patients diagnosed with
      uncontrolled hypertension and at least one antihypertensive medication. Those patients with
      significant sleep apnea wil be randomized to CPAP or nasal strips for 6 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
